Class AbstractFeatureManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.robopupu.api.dependency.ScopedObject
      • com.robopupu.api.plugin.AbstractPluginComponent

          • com.robopupu.api.feature.AbstractFeatureManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.app.Application.ActivityLifecycleCallbacks, Manager, Scopeable, FeatureManager, PluginComponent

    public abstract class AbstractFeatureManager
extends AbstractManager
implements FeatureManager, android.app.Application.ActivityLifecycleCallbacks
    AbstractFeatureManager provides a default implementation of FeatureManager.
